    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1992年11月末。波兰东部一个与世隔绝的小镇遭遇了一场可怕的灾难，慢慢地开始吞噬它所接触到的所有人和东西。这是你的朋友巴泰克不接你电话前最后的行踪。现在，你需要跟随他的脚步找出他最初来到这个小镇的原因，很有可能他这趟旅程永远无法离开。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索附魔城镇<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235430/extras/5b0dc3f147e6c321dde214083b241d75.poster.avif?t=1771346776\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235430/extras/5b0dc3f147e6c321dde214083b241d75.webm?t=1771346776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235430/extras/5b0dc3f147e6c321dde214083b241d75.mp4?t=1771346776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杰西奥内-科洛尼亚镇的情况非常不对劲。探索一个阴森恐怖的、与世隔绝的90年代波兰小镇，该镇已被某些邪恶力量所吞噬。街上到处都是某种肮脏的黏液。这里的人、建筑和野生动物似乎都在从内部慢慢侵蚀恶化。你得找到失踪的朋友，并在这个小镇对你也伸出魔爪之前赶紧离开。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与深不可测的怪兽搏斗并生存下来</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235430/extras/12dc2f55855bf280d9b46296de0a00a7.poster.avif?t=1771346776\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235430/extras/12dc2f55855bf280d9b46296de0a00a7.webm?t=1771346776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235430/extras/12dc2f55855bf280d9b46296de0a00a7.mp4?t=1771346776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找稀缺的物资和武器，击退游荡在城镇最黑暗角落的丑陋怪物。你不是英雄，但你的求生意志仍然强大到足以度过这场噩梦。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与逐渐失去理智的当地人交谈</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些疑问或谜题只能由当地人回答。但他们很少对外人有帮助。如果你想了解他们，你必须假装融入他们的幻想，了解他们的内心世界。在这个空荡荡的小镇上，那些仍然清醒的人似乎在生与死之间徘徊。他们封闭的心灵逐渐走向疯狂，而你的问题毫无疑问地开始刺激到他们破碎的神经…… </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现代科技与狠活加持的经典视效</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235430/extras/49a39423ca9045c9e9681b4bf5bd2b5e.poster.avif?t=1771346776\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235430/extras/49a39423ca9045c9e9681b4bf5bd2b5e.webm?t=1771346776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235430/extras/49a39423ca9045c9e9681b4bf5bd2b5e.mp4?t=1771346776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的内部定制技术另辟蹊径为像素外观带来创新表现。手绘像素艺术环境现在通过动态照明和自由相机旋转系统，让你从八个不同的角度探索世界。只是不要让那些阴影在你的脑海中作怪。 </p>",
